HIV_original %>% 
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>%
  filter(word %in% c("t.co","https", "http", "hivprevention", "amp") == FALSE) %>%
  anti_join(get_stopwords()) %>%
  count(year, word, sort = TRUE) %>%
  bind_tf_idf(word, year, n) %>% 
  mutate(word = fct_reorder(word, tf_idf)) %>%
  group_by(year) %>% 
  top_n(15, tf_idf) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(word = reorder(word, tf_idf)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(word, tf_idf, fill = year)) +
  geom_col(show.legend = FALSE) +
  labs(x = NULL, y = "tf-idf") +
  facet_wrap(~year, ncol = 2, scales = "free") +
  coord_flip()
library(topicmodels)
HIV_dtm <- HIV_original %>%
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>%
  anti_join(get_stopwords()) %>%
  filter(word %in% c("t.co","https", "http", "hivprevention", "amp") == FALSE) %>%
  count(year, word) %>%
  cast_dtm(year, word,n)

HIV_lda <- LDA(HIV_dtm, k =4, control=list(seed=1234))
HIV_topics <- tidy(HIV_lda, matrix="beta")
HIV_top_terms <- HIV_topics %>%
  group_by(topic) %>% 
  top_n(10,beta) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  arrange(topic, -beta)
HIV_top_terms %>%
  mutate(term = reorder_within(term, beta, topic)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(term, beta, fill = factor(topic))) +
  geom_col(show.legend = FALSE) +
  facet_wrap(~ topic, scales = "free") +
  coord_flip() +
  scale_x_reordered()
